{
  "texts": [
    "For each exercise assigned by the teacher, students in the treatment group had access to a chat with GPT4.",
    "While GPT4 had access to the exercise via its prompt, students did not see the original exercise from the teacher.",
    "In both treatment and control conditions, students could access the platform at any time.",
    "We did not enforce a minimum or maximum level of engagement.",
    "The teacher could not observe the content of the student's solution."
  ]
}